are arguing,

247
00:14:13,485 --> 00:14:16,045
the easiest way
to win the war

248
00:14:16,121 --> 00:14:18,282
is to emancipate slaves,

249
00:14:18,357 --> 00:14:20,484
and they make
a brilliant point

250
00:14:20,559 --> 00:14:24,120
that eventually the Lincoln
Administration accepts,

251
00:14:24,196 --> 00:14:26,130
