the economically volatile years

778
00:44:15,185 --> 00:44:20,179
after Reconstruction left
the family mired in debt.

779
00:44:20,257 --> 00:44:25,422
Now, Isaiah was determined to
build a haven for black people

780
00:44:25,496 --> 00:44:29,125
in a remote corner
of Mississippi.

781
00:44:29,199 --> 00:44:31,929
FIELD: The Delta was
a majority-black region

782
00:44:32,002 --> 00:44:34,937
that was largely unsettled.

783
00:44:35,005 --> 00:44:37,439
Isaiah Montgomery saw
himself as improving

784
00:44:37,508 --> 00:44:39,408
upon his father's dream,

785
00:44:39,476 --> 00:44:42,912
and he improved upon it
by making this

786
00:44:42,980 --> 00:44:45,915
a paradise
for black landowners.

787
00:44:45,983 --> 00:44:51,421
GATES: Isaiah would call
his new town Mound Bayou.

788
00:44:51,488 --> 00:44:55,891
It was a self-contained,
all-black wand.

789
00:44:57,661 --> 00:45:00,596
