792
00:45:07,237 --> 00:45:09,671
and the constant threat
of violence that pervaded

793
00:45:09,740 --> 00:45:12,675
most Southern towns
by this point

794
00:45:12,743 --> 00:45:15,576
is simply unimaginable.

795
00:45:17,181 --> 00:45:20,617
