892
00:50:25,622 --> 00:50:28,056
that he was indistinguishable
from whites.

893
00:50:28,125 --> 00:50:31,060
GATES: Why did they need
a guy light and bright
and damn-n ear white?

894
00:50:31,128 --> 00:50:34,063
BROWN: What they wanted
to do is to tell the courts

895
00:50:34,131 --> 00:50:36,565
