922
00:51:51,975 --> 00:51:55,411
Now, the law relegated
African Americans

923
00:51:55,479 --> 00:51:58,880
to the margins
of white society.

924
00:51:58,949 --> 00:52:01,440
Free? Yes.

925
00:52:01,518 --> 00:52:03,918
Equal? No.

926
00:52:06,523 --> 00:52:10,960
